      <h2>what is diabetes？</h2>
      <p>
        Diabetes is a serious condition where your blood glucose level is too
        high. It can happen when your body doesn’t produce enough insulin or the
        insulin it produces isn’t effective. Or, when your body can’t produce
        any insulin at all.
      </p>
