  <h2>Managing Diabetes</h2>
  <p>The common symptoms of diabetes include:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>
      Get the information you need. The more you know, the more confident you
      will become and and the easier it will be to manage your diabetes.
    </li>
    <li>
      Recognise your role: take some personal responsibility for managing your
      diabetes day-to-day
    </li>
    <li>
      Be honest: give accurate information about your health and how you are
      really feeling.
    </li>
    <li>
